{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/netty/netty/issues/11379","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/netty/netty","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/netty/netty/issues/11379/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/netty/netty/issues/11379/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/netty/netty/issues/11379/events","html_url":"https://github.com/netty/netty/issues/11379","id":917218686,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU5MTcyMTg2ODY=","number":11379,"title":"[codec-mqtt] Netty tries to interpret QOS level on CONNECT package","user":{"login":"hylkevds","id":4989461,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ5ODk0NjE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4989461?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds","html_url":"https://github.com/hylkevds","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hylkevds/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/netty/netty/milestones/241","html_url":"https://github.com/netty/netty/milestone/241","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/netty/netty/milestones/241/labels","id":6773106,"node_id":"MDk6TWlsZXN0b25lNjc3MzEwNg==","number":241,"title":"4.1.66.Final","description":"","creator":{"login":"normanmaurer","id":439362,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzOTM2Mg==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/439362?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer","html_url":"https://github.com/normanmaurer","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"open_issues":0,"closed_issues":123,"state":"closed","created_at":"2021-05-19T09:14:30Z","updated_at":"2022-06-03T05:00:03Z","due_on":null,"closed_at":"2021-07-16T09:56:14Z"},"comments":3,"created_at":"2021-06-10T11:09:02Z","updated_at":"2021-06-16T13:00:11Z","closed_at":"2021-06-16T12:59:16Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"The MQTT CONNECT package FIXED header contains only the MQTT Control Packet type in the first 4 bits. The remaining bits in the first byte are reserved. ([SPEC](http://docs.oasis-open.org/mqtt/mqtt/v3.1.1/errata01/os/mqtt-v3.1.1-errata01-os-complete.html#_Toc442180841))\r\nCurrently, the MqttDecoder parses the fixed header the same for all packet types, and thus tries to interpret the reserved bits of the fixed header in the CONNECT packet:\r\nhttps://github.com/netty/netty/blob/c78afbc4f13ac4d6cb488fb14b31379960f03fff/codec-mqtt/src/main/java/io/netty/handler/codec/mqtt/MqttDecoder.java#L166\r\n https://github.com/netty/netty/blob/c78afbc4f13ac4d6cb488fb14b31379960f03fff/codec-mqtt/src/main/java/io/netty/handler/codec/mqtt/MqttDecoder.java#L185 \r\n\r\nApparently, the HiveMQ client sets the remaining bits to all 1, resulting the MqttDecoder to try to interpret bits 2 + 3 of the reserved bits as \"QOS 3\" resulting in an exception.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nIgnore reserved bits\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\ntries to interpret reserved bits, resulting in an exception.\r\nCaused by: java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: invalid QoS: 3\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nSend a CONNECT packet with the reserved bits set to 1\r\n\r\n### Minimal yet complete reproducer code (or URL to code)\r\nWorking on it\r\n\r\n### Netty version\r\nnetty-4.1.65\r\n\r\n### JVM version (e.g. `java -version`)\r\n11\r\n\r\n### OS version (e.g. `uname -a`)\r\nLinux\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"normanmaurer","id":439362,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzOTM2Mg==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/439362?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer","html_url":"https://github.com/normanmaurer","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/normanmaurer/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/netty/netty/issues/11379/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-